{"tid":1764282,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"葉劉淑儀: 政府以為區議會選舉會帶來和平是大錯特錯 反對派的氣燄只會愈趨囂張","createTime":"2019-12-01T04:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T07:06:00.000Z","uid":167469,"like":219,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"3e92e5cb846f132762348ddad9da3600a0bdc596","tid":1764282,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"<ins>Anti-government victory in Hong Kong&rsquo;s district council elections won&rsquo;t bring about peace(節錄)</ins><br />\n<br />\nThe mass turnout of angry and young voters swept away a large number of pro-establishment district councillors with solid district work. The pro-establishment camp held on to just 59 seats &ndash; a record low, thus ceding control of the district council seats on the Election Committee to the pan-dems in the next election, due in 2022.<br />\n<br />\nA relative calm returned in the days preceding polling on November 24. But rallies on all manner of causes, including thanking the US for passing legislation to impose sanctions on Hong Kong, immediately followed.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Emboldened by the electoral success of anti-government candidates, including many who had stood with the rioters, the successful holding of the district council elections &ndash; viewed by a self-congratulatory government as an achievement &ndash; will not bring peace.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Rather, the rioters, and their behind-the-scenes backers, will become more aggressive in pressing their demands. Their supporters may soon have to live with the consequences of legitimising street violence and discrimination against compatriots of mainland Chinese origin.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3039891/anti-government-victory-hong-kongs-district-council-elections-wont\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fcomment%2Fopinion%2Farticle%2F3039891%2Fanti-government-victory-hong-kongs-district-council-elections-wont&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=94bbd9df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3039891/anti-government-victory-hong-kongs-district-council-elections-wont</a>"},{"pid":"662e594a4da1b30c674cca63d179f11ef34ea7d3","tid":1764282,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"72bd33cb56a4cdf75a0b50c2e42a680c8a7d2ade","tid":1764282,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"95b7984e6a361bdff81c7554422a43693863ce20","tid":1764282,"uid":103230,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"係滅黨仆晒街啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a7da78c587c637ffd787321e2c8230b6927256","tid":1764282,"uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"佢嬲豬"},{"pid":"5bd2010b82148e20d49f3aa72141549312b594b5","tid":1764282,"uid":167548,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">謝了</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"94e565898e54956a71044a3b445788a551d0b7cd","tid":1764282,"uid":41771,"like":159,"dislike":0,"score":159,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJUebcJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJUebcJ.jpg&h=b686c6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20f1AEu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20f1AEu.png&h=4aa439e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7503712841c3dd5df4224d0b2efdedffc1b2fa05","tid":1764282,"uid":121197,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01